            <span class="highlight"><strong>retired</strong> software engineer</span>
            based in Taguig City, Philippines. I have 10 years of experience in 
            developing software, mainly web applications.
          %p
            This is my mini-portfolio website where you can <a href="#portfolio">browse</a> 
            a small sample of my work. You could also check what <a href="#skills">skills</a> 
            I used to offer.
