            I guess you have some time on your hands since you're still reading this. In that case, you might want to head over to the <a href="#bio">bio</a> section to know more about me. If you <em>really</em> have a lot of time on your hands, why not head over to <a href="http://blog.bryanbibat.net">my blog</a> and read about the geeky stuff I'm into. I also have a <a href="https://leanpub.com/u/bryanbibat">bookstore</a> over at Leanpub where I'm crowdfunding future books. 

